DataHandler -> DataHandler: Load training data
DataHandler -> DataHandler: Preprocess features
DataHandler -> Model: Initialize parameters (slope, intercept)
Model -> Model: Set initial weights randomly
Model -> Optimizer: Configure learning rate
Optimizer -> Model: Request current parameters
Model -> Optimizer: Return current weights
Optimizer -> DataHandler: Request training batch
DataHandler -> Optimizer: Return X, y batch
Optimizer -> Model: Forward pass with batch
Model -> Optimizer: Return predictions
Optimizer -> Optimizer: Calculate cost function
Optimizer -> Optimizer: Compute gradients
Optimizer -> Model: Update parameters
Model -> Model: Apply weight updates
Optimizer -> Optimizer: Check convergence criteria
Optimizer -> Model: Forward pass (validation)
Model -> Optimizer: Return final predictions
Optimizer -> DataHandler: Training complete